{"id": "1418057921350205490", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "2\n突撃を初手で使い、超次元に収納する", "timestamp": "2025-09-18T02:15:54.692000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1418059164348846091", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "3\nそれ以降は超次元の収納に余計なものは極力いれないように注意する\n入れた場合はカーシアで取り出す", "timestamp": "2025-09-18T02:20:51.046000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-18T02:25:14.185000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1418059308137971854", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "4\n黒渦の再利用ができるようになったら、突撃を取り出して突撃を使い収納しなおす", "timestamp": "2025-09-18T02:21:25.328000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1418059399477461044", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "(MAPありの場合、戦闘毎に初手で突撃ができる)", "timestamp": "2025-09-18T02:21:47.105000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1418059610652151809", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "5\n超次元は属性統一の場合、超次元に収納時の威力の強化が＋25%多くなるので、染めた方が強い場合が多い", "timestamp": "2025-09-18T02:22:37.453000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1418060075938877502", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "(深海を混ぜたメリット、耐久が強くなり怒涛と突撃が相性○)\n(狂魔を混ぜたメリット、MAPありの場合の遺物に強いものがある、狂気の回転が上がる)\n(混沌を混ぜたメリット、キーオーダーくらい)", "timestamp": "2025-09-18T02:24:28.386000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1418060868897210500", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "だいたいこの動きを意識したら強いです👍", "timestamp": "2025-09-18T02:27:37.442000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1418063538039165011", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "331646504856977409", "author_name": "kyubiiiin", "author_bot": false, "content": "ありがとうございます、やってみます！\nアドバイス頂いた通り一旦超次元で染めてみようと思います(  . .)\"", "timestamp": "2025-09-18T02:38:13.815000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["438289046993633281"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1418060868897210500", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1418064387645771916", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "パーティ内にダメージ強化を多めにつけると全体の火力が上がるので突撃の威力も上がります\n界域知識は超次元収納した威力の伸び幅が上がります\n染めてない場合は一切あげなくて良い、染めた場合は上げる価値ある", "timestamp": "2025-09-18T02:41:36.377000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["331646504856977409"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1418063538039165011", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1418069906783600780", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "797509921343275038", "author_name": "8106ne", "author_bot": false, "content": "1ターン目、集結、\n2ターン目で突撃して取り出して集結を意識してたんだけど、\n1ターン目集結取り出しのがいいのかな？\n\n2ターン目で終わるから。。？3ターン以上続く時もですかね。", "timestamp": "2025-09-18T03:03:32.242000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["438289046993633281"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1418057722984923258", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1418070533370544260", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "初手集結だしいれのメリット\n2ターン目に収納用の突撃と、トドメor削り用の弱突撃が使える\n初手集結しないメリット\n強めの突撃を後でも出来る\nデメリット\n突撃で倒し切った場合に集結が収納に残る\n同一戦闘が長引く場合、次回黒渦を使用できるターンが遠のく", "timestamp": "2025-09-18T03:06:01.632000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["797509921343275038"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🤝", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1418069906783600780", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1418070794864558181", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "※\nカーシアで初手収納取り出しを黒渦を使わずにできた場合\n強い突撃を3ターン目に再度とりだし収納ができる", "timestamp": "2025-09-18T03:07:03.977000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-18T03:07:16.698000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1418071281693098169", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "797509921343275038", "author_name": "8106ne", "author_bot": false, "content": "黒渦の回転と弱突いるか、\n何ターン続くかあたりで臨機応変にすね。。！\n集結してる間ノーガードでやられてるのは立ち回りでみんなどうカバーしてるのか気になる。。", "timestamp": "2025-09-18T03:09:00.046000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1418071525470507160", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "1ターン目の被ダメは気にせん", "timestamp": "2025-09-18T03:09:58.167000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1418071681834029087", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "次回以降の戦闘は突撃を初手から使えるから楽だし", "timestamp": "2025-09-18T03:10:35.447000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🤝", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
